<div class="section" id="opensource">
  <h2>Open Source</h2>
  <p>
    Hidim is still in its infancy and it could use your help!  You can help by trying it out, 
    <a href="http://github.com/mnutt/hid.im-firefox/issues">finding and reporting bugs</a>, 
    <a href="http://github.com/mnutt/hid.im-firefox">hacking on the source</a> or creating 
    implementations in other languages. Hidim is licensed under the <a href="http://github.com/mnutt/hid.im-firefox/raw/4cdb119fe6233674dc3f1e31f9f17ea94445107a/LICENSE">MIT License</a>.
  </p>

